&lt;p&gt;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/sindresorhus/gulp-imagemin/releases/tag/v8.0.0&#34;&gt;https://github.com/sindresorhus/gulp-imagemin/releases/tag/v8.0.0&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
